LogicalColumn.name: # of Products
LogicalColumn.Description: Distinct # of products purchased by the Company.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 30000 THEN '<$30,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 60000 THEN '$30,000 - $60,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 90000 THEN '$60,000 - $90,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 120000 THEN '$90,000 - $120,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" >= 120000 THEN '>$120,000' ELSE 'Unspecified' END

LogicalColumn.name: Household Label Name
LogicalColumn.Description: Household Label Name. e.g. Mr & Mrs Smith

LogicalColumn.name: Household Salutation
LogicalColumn.Description: Household Salutation. e.g Dear Mr & Mrs Smith

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Dim - Household"."Last COG Payment Date" > "Core"."Dim - Household"."Last Cash Gift Date" THEN "Core"."Dim - Household"."Last COG Payment Date" ELSE "Core"."Dim - Household"."Last Cash Gift Date" END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Household"."Potential Value", 0) + IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Household"."Historical Value", 0) + IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Household"."Future Value", 0) - IFNULL("Core"."Dim - Household"."Cost Value", 0)

LogicalColumn.name: Primary Canvasser
LogicalColumn.Description: The name of the employee who is currently canvassing this household and is ticked as ‘Primary’ in Siebel

LogicalColumn.name: Primary Canvasser Team
LogicalColumn.Description: The team to which the Primary Canvasser currently belongs

LogicalColumn.name: VF Regional Canvasser
LogicalColumn.Description: The Canvasser who is responsible for the area in which the household's primary address sits, as defined in the Postcode Admin table on Siebel

LogicalColumn.name: VF Region Name
LogicalColumn.Description: The VF Region which the postal district belongs to as defined in the Postcode Admin table on Siebel e.g. PL14 is in Region 9

LogicalColumn.name: Opportunity Confirmed Date
LogicalColumn.Description: The date that the Opportunity reached the 'Confirmed' stage

LogicalColumn.name: Reconfirmed Date
LogicalColumn.Description: The date that the commitment was last confirmed. For Legacies, this is when the pledge was last confirmed to be in place

LogicalColumn.name: Reconfirmed Source
LogicalColumn.Description: The source of the reconfirmation of the commitment. For Legacies, this is the source that led to the pledge being confirmed

LogicalColumn.name: Reconfirmed Source Description
LogicalColumn.Description: The source of the reconfirmation of the commitment. For Legacies, this is the source that led to the pledge being confirmed

LogicalColumn.name: Pledge Type
LogicalColumn.Description: The pledge product. Where there are multiple pledge products on the opportunity, this will be 'Multiple'

LogicalColumn.name: Percentage
LogicalColumn.Description: For Legacies, this is the percentage of the owning party's estate that they have stipulated must be left to CRUK in their will.

LogicalColumn.name: # FWS Uses
LogicalColumn.Description: Number of times the Free Will Service has been used

LogicalColumn.name: First Will Date
LogicalColumn.Description: Will Date from the household's first opportunity

LogicalColumn.name: First Agreed Amount

LogicalColumn.name: Last Will Date
LogicalColumn.Description: Will Date from the household's latest opportunity

LogicalColumn.name: Last Agreed Amount

LogicalColumn.name: Last Opportunity Confirmed Date
LogicalColumn.Description: The date that the Last Opportunity reached the 'Confirmed' stage

LogicalColumn.name: Legacy Region
